parameters: Rade: Kyaaain! You came for me~!
Rade: Luuna, bring some sweet treats, will you~?
Rade: Ugh... It's none of our business~.

Rade: Good work to you all as well. Let the fools kill each other as
they please. Kyahaha~
Rade: What's up~? Did you bring me some sweets~?
Rade: Hmm~? You want me to look at a pretty stone~?

Becky: Hey, Rade, you must know something, right? About this stone
with high magical power.
Rade: I told you~ I wanted sweets, didn't I~? What's with this rock~?
Rade: Hmm~, it does seem like a special stone~.

Rade: Kyahaha! I see~. If this stone sells for a lot, you're saying we
can buy sweets with the money~.
Luuna: No, that's not really what I meant...

Rade: Well, first we need to check what kind of stone it is~. It
certainly doesn't seem like an ordinary stone~.
Rade: Kyahaha! Let's go appraise it~♪
Rade: Mufufu~♪ Let's examine the stone~.
Rade: What! What! What's this~! I've been cursed~!
Rade: Hmm~! My magic has been sealed~...

Rade: Sigh... It looks like I won't be able to use magic for a few
weeks~...

Rade: It seems like the curse was supposed to prevent me from using
magic for generations, but~... Sigh...

Rade: I think I can manage to break the curse in a few weeks
though~...
Rade: Ugyu---! What have you guys brought me~!

Becky: Well, it's fine. If she can't use magic, maybe she'll be a bit
quieter for a change.

Cain: That Rade, even with her magic sealed, she still talks in that
cutesy way. She's not really panicking, is she?

Becky: Right~ Let's just leave her be. It's probably some kind of
divine punishment.

Luuna: ............(I hope Rade-san will be okay. It would be bad if
she got attacked by bandits or something...)
Rade: Haa... This is the worst...

Rade: Ugh! Haa... Fine then. I'll behave since I think the curse will
be lifted if I do...
Rade: Ugh! Mind your own business. Just disappear already.
The magic-less Rade... One night, such a trial awaited her.

While Rade was asleep, the remnants of the bandits she had defeated
came for her.

Normally, Rade would have instantly killed the bandits, but now she
was powerless...

Even the mighty Rade had no choice but to obediently follow the
bandits.

Rade: (To think I'm being blackmailed with lewd photos by those
guys...~n... It's too embarrassing to say...~n...)
Rade: Geez! I said it's nothing...~n...
I'm worried... (Can you work in a brothel?)
The magic-less Rade... One night, such a trial awaited her.

While Rade was asleep, the remnants of the bandits she had defeated
came for her.

Normally, Rade would have instantly killed the bandits, but now she
was powerless...

Even the mighty Rade had no choice but to obediently follow the
bandits' orders.
Rade: I'm telling you it's nothing. Now go away...~n... Haa...

Rade was being blackmailed by the bandits with erotic photos they had
taken of her.

As compensation for the bandits she had defeated, the bandits ordered
Rade to work in a brothel.

Without her magic, Rade had no choice but to do as the bandits said
for the time being.

\I[7]HINT】Rade can now work at the brothel. You can choose between
"Brothel Room" or "Call Girl" from the brothel owner. You can select
from "???".

[Servant] A gift for Lady Rade doesn't have to be sweet treats; any
present that seems to delight her will do. Please find something
wonderful during your adventure.

*During your adventure, there are "Gifts for Rade" in treasure chests
and various places. If you obtain a gift and give it to Rade, you
might receive something in return.
Servant: Hmm... It seems all four locations have been conquered.
Luuna: But we still haven't encountered Regnus Grahardt.
Becky: Sigh... Back to square one, I guess.
Rade: Kyahaha~! All that effort for nothing~!

Becky: Ugh... This girl... You're looking for Regnus Grahardt too,
aren't you?
Luuna: Servant, what should we do now...

Servant: Hmm... I'm not sure. It's none of our business, but somehow I
feel responsible.

Cain: No point in moping around here. Let's head to the tavern in Bell
City and blow off some steam.
Becky: Right. Let's regroup and strategize in Bell City.

Servant: There are four places where traces of Lord Regnus Grahardt
have been found. After conquering all four, please speak to me.
1,「イーザのピラミッド」に行く。
※未攻略の箇所を聞く／地図を見る
Servant: The Pyramid of Eeza remains unconquered.
Servant: The Tower of Beren remains unconquered.
Servant: The Temple of Rima remains unconquered.
Servant: The Boro Mines remain unconquered.

Servant: There are dungeons that must be conquered in these four
locations.

Servant: "I'm sorry for not being of help. Luuna-san, I'm personally
rooting for you."
Luuna: Rade-san, I've made some sweets and brought them for you.
Rade: Kyain~! My sweets~! I've been so looking forward to this~!
Rade: Munch munch munch munch... munch munch munch munch...
Rade: What is it~n? I'm munching right now, you know~n
Luuna: I want you to become my master and teach me magic, Rade-san.

Becky: Hey, Rade! She made sweets and brought them over! At least help
out a little!

Becky: Seriously... You have servants as disciples. Is Luuna not good
enough?

Rade: Not good enough~n. I don't like the motivation~n. Saving the
country or village or whatever is just trivial~n. Not interested~n.

Luuna: No, it's not just that. The real reason is... there's more to
it.

Luuna: I... this is also for myself. I really don't want to rely on
Regnus Grahardt or Rade-san's power. It's frustrating... saving the
village is just an excuse... the truth is I...

Rade: With that~ I understand you now. You don't need to say
everything~n.
Becky: Huh... What did you understand from that?

Rade: If that's the reason, then it's fine~n. You're too much of a
goody-two-shoes for a coward, and I didn't like that~n.

Rade: Plus~ according to my judgment~n. It seems like you're hiding
your true power~n. That kind of thing gives me thrills~n. Kyaa-n!

Rade: Ugyu-n! I'm a little interested in you now~n! But~? I'll only be
your master for one day, okay~n?

Luuna: Thank you so much. So you'll be my master for just one day. I
want you to teach me various things right away.

Luuna: Ah... come to think of it, Rade-san, you can't use magic right
now, can you?

Rade: It's okay~n. It seems like I can use magic just for today~n. I
forcefully broke the curse, and since I'm feeling good today, I think
I can use magic~n.

Rade: I think the curse will be lifted in about a week anyway~n.
Kyaa-n!
Luuna: That's great. Then let's get started right away...
